This project is in no way affiliated, nor endorsed by Hypixel.

You must follow their rules when using any assets hosted in any branch of this repo, with "main" being the only exception as it doesn't contain any.

This repo is only intended to allow for easy access to unpacked versions and to keep track of any changes made between versions.

You can find the pack for a specific Minecraft version in the branch for that version, additionally, there are alpha/<version> branches which contain the latest alpha changes.

26.2 - Stable: https://github.com/meowdding/hypixel-pack/tree/26.2
26.2 - Alpha: https://github.com/meowdding/hypixel-pack/tree/alpha/26.2